<ul><li><cite id="CITEREFSmith" class="citation web cs1">Smith, Christopher. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080513184644/http://www.lejendary.com/la/template.php?page=garygygax&amp;style=blaze">"An Interview with Gary Gygax"</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.lejendary.com/la/template.php?page=garygygax&amp;style=blaze">the original</a> on May 13, 2008<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">August 15,</span> 2005</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=An+Interview+with+Gary+Gygax&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Christopher&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lejendary.com%2Fla%2Ftemplate.php%3Fpage%3Dgarygygax%26style%3Dblaze&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGary+Gygax" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></li>
<li><cite id="CITEREFScott_Lynch2001" class="citation web cs1">Scott Lynch (May 1, 2001). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20071009233259/http://www.rpg.net/news+reviews/columns/lynch01may01.html">"Interview with Gary Gygax"</a>. RPGnet. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.rpg.net/news+reviews/columns/lynch01may01.html">the original</a> on October 9, 2007.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Interview+with+Gary+Gygax&amp;rft.pub=RPGnet&amp;rft.date=2001-05-01&amp;rft.au=Scott+Lynch&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rpg.net%2Fnews%2Breviews%2Fcolumns%2Flynch01may01.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGary+Gygax" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></li>
